{"tid":259180,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"因為一隻甲由 我隻貓驚左我。。。","createTime":"2017-05-26T16:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T01:47:10.000Z","uid":192,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0861b3262a6fd56eeaf543082f4fa743c2c11b","tid":259180,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"頭先見到勁大隻甲由係我間房<br />\n我即刻精神崩緊係咁叫我隻貓去捉<br />\n我好慌張咁用隻手指住個個位係咁叫<br />\n隻甲由係個到啊！！！<br />\n點知隻貓唔望不特止以為我痴左線<br />\n跟住仲夾硬抱佢埋去點知隻甲由又走得快<br />\n隻貓驚左我之後匿埋我比零食都唔出黎<br />\n我都心諗我自己搞點算 甲由入我房真係唔敢訓<br />\n等左陣隻甲由終於係我衣櫃出黎<br />\n我事前揀左本我唔會要既書<br />\n打左第一下唔中 打第二下先中<br />\n<br />\n宜家隻甲由就係本書下面唔想拎走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/002750_80b0a649ceb14374f2317385b55c6bec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F002750_80b0a649ceb14374f2317385b55c6bec.jpg&h=a020b3c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad7a8dc692a18c71fd6d89ef700e80c3892fe04a","tid":259180,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"一陣等屋企人返黎幫我整<br />\n我睇下影唔影到條屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afa64b27edaca10d76f7cada1c8bd3b4573b4e9","tid":259180,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:31:45.000Z","msg":"留名跟進貓貓情況"},{"pid":"aebd277befc09bb3779c627048933201dec02710","tid":259180,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:34:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾熱狗樓豬又想攪分化<br />\n垃圾PoSt唔洗覆"},{"pid":"c581bf2ee24548cdd1e5ea3b698920302439066a","tid":259180,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾熱狗樓豬又想攪分化<br />\n垃圾PoSt唔洗覆</blockquote><br />\n做咩9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ec5dce8a7f4f25f9021ed986c48448b8cead39","tid":259180,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"叫貓食屍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa0d16094c8427466c6b1d3cc8d9a6c3e19261c","tid":259180,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:38:45.000Z","msg":"通常我隻貓主動去搵強<br />\n不過唔知係我好彩定d強唔知係邊冇出黎 <br />\n呢幾年都係見過幾次only<br />\n通常佢玩到隻強反肚就我去執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n噴多次殺蟲水確定真係死撚哂先拎d垃圾剷剷去垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 任何昆蟲都好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a59bdf1c9889b3c3ecedf3f8937075f0e11b963","tid":259180,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/004123_a604bb4b568a41eab21b1356df599eab.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F004123_a604bb4b568a41eab21b1356df599eab.jpg&d=LtIbkOcu3DY%2FoUE7XZdWtttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=845c6241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/004123_a604bb4b568a41eab21b1356df599eab.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9020c771bf70a1e21172600eb10dc5e40847d820","tid":259180,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0709659adfee8768b4cacec591194bd828f4acb6","tid":259180,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常我隻貓主動去搵強<br />\n不過唔知係我好彩定d強唔知係邊冇出黎 <br />\n呢幾年都係見過幾次only<br />\n通常佢玩到隻強反肚就我去執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n噴多次殺蟲水確定真係死撚哂先拎d垃圾剷剷去垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 任何昆蟲都好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我隻貓捉開細強多<br />\n大強我都少見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d874b1ed1383a19bc5bfe8a9bce8a6b60e68dcff","tid":259180,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:44:02.000Z","msg":"返去溫書考dse吧啦"},{"pid":"cf1b3adf8a1f78416b62c264860e18684a451d41","tid":259180,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:44:53.000Z","msg":"唔好咁廢啦<br />\n我用一格廁紙殺一隻德國強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你居然要搵貓幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc18a9c44125ef7186af83885f3770ce2ff2a806","tid":259180,"uid":29219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:45:27.000Z","msg":"咁樣賣廣告都第一次見"},{"pid":"4c9bcaf41aa9a09a5c4fcd1bb3c794eb552dd4ff","tid":259180,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好咁廢啦<br />\n我用一格廁紙殺一隻德國強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你居然要搵貓幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德國強係咪細細隻個d啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4921096d758f9fbf3c54b3bfcecedddcbce3e0","tid":259180,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樣賣廣告都第一次見</blockquote><br />\n我一次都冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90093afab9c363b1dcbe27e67da8edb731cd3e3d","tid":259180,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"必殺攻略 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae9ea0067d1a306fca19208518bb7131ba16cfc","tid":259180,"uid":69791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:49:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2a61c1edba94b19b489333911c0d34c420e3419","tid":259180,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:55:46.000Z","msg":"名師果然係killer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaca7fb2f86317074163cbaf67658725b975b7a9","tid":259180,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:10:45.000Z","msg":"養貓十幾廿年 一隻小強都未見過"},{"pid":"e121262b8d9d814c2537017de2aaebc3a01ba3d8","tid":259180,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:13:50.000Z","msg":"見到本書笑左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7c355088a916d8630d3c41c21f8f63194c54d1","tid":259180,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:09:54.000Z","msg":"天書正確用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4d1afb49135e775ebbe2a132628ef13ae856c0","tid":259180,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天書正確用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n救左我一命"},{"pid":"c4f90ac920566273c43d1c607a1cbe477595c856","tid":259180,"uid":4408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:48:35.000Z","msg":"廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93118561c42789daffe6af29e7ebb1eb4af24857","tid":259180,"uid":19542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:50:27.000Z","msg":"我隻貓自動自覺去捉 仲會抆左隻甲由腳慢慢折磨佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3180ae07ef0f96c74fe2100979bbcdd275d2ba35","tid":259180,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T19:14:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻貓自動自覺去捉 仲會抆左隻甲由腳慢慢折磨佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貓捉曱甴係為咗玩<br />\n佢唔會食曱甴但會㩒住佢抆腳<br />\n或者由佢跑兩跑又捉返返嚟<br />\n隻強唔係獵物而只係玩具<br />\n玩死咗佢就唔會理等有下隻"}]}